Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: GPT-friendly CLI for summarizing directory trees and file content
 GPTree is a CLI utility that converts directory structures and file contents
 into GPT-friendly prompts or summaries. Useful for context-aware LLM usage.
 